      "description": "Available is a well-sorted E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 straight-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system. This example delivers a visceral driving experience through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from recent bushing refreshes and a documented subframe inspection. While showing honest signs of spirited use, the mechanical integrity is paramount, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a smooth power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A true driver\u2019s machine for the purist.",
